snippet.title: Wrestling Empire: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
As much as I would have liked to salvage something from 2020, my first Nintendo game at least had the honour of kick-starting the indie uprising of 2021:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/wrestling-empire-switch/
